org.lukep.javavis.program.generic.models
Class ProjectModel

java.lang.Object
  org.lukep.javavis.program.generic.models.ProjectModel
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable, IMeasurableNode, IGenericModelNode, IProgramSourceObserver
public class ProjectModel
extends java.lang.Object
implements IProgramSourceObserver

This is the root node of the entire abstract program model tree - the project. It contains references to all of the packages and all of the classes within the currently loaded project.

See Also:
